son.Category }}</td> </tr>  </table>  <p> Please note that this decision applies only to this specific role and is not a reflection of your overall abilities or potential. We encourage you to continue developing your skills and to apply again for future opportunities that align with your experience and career goals. </p>  <p> We will keep your profile in our talent database and may contact you if a suitable position becomes available in the future. </p>  <p> We wish you every success in your career and thank you once again for considering our organization. </p>  <p> Best regards,<br><br>  <strong>Human Resources Team</strong><br> Recruitment Department  </p>  </div>  <div class=\"footer\"> This is an automated email generated by our AI Recruitment System.<br> Please do not reply directly to this message. </div>  </div>  </body> </html>",
